headline: How To Earn $500 A Month From Philip Morris Stock Ahead Of Q1 Earnings
summary: Philip Morris International Inc. (NYSE:PM) will release its first-quarter financial results before the opening bell on Wednesday, April 23. Analysts expect the company to report quarterly earnings at $1.61 per share, up from $1.50 per share in the year-ago period. According to data from Benzinga Pro, Philip Morris International projects quarterly revenue of $9.14 billion, compared to $8.79 billion a year earlier. On April 16, Citigroup analyst Simon Hales maintained Philip Morris Intl with a Buy
